text: Camren Renee Bicondova (born May 22, 1999) is an American actress, dancer and model. Bicondova is best known for her role as young Selina Kyle/Catwoman on the Fox television series Gotham. ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:American dancers Category:Models from San Diego Category:Actors from San Diego Category:American child actors Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors
